:

1. *Dosad* sam se baš dobro proveo. (So far I had a great time.) 
2. *Dosadno* mi je bilo sinoć. (I was bored last night.)
3. Do sada nisam čuo za taj problem. (I haven't heard about this problem so far.) 
4. *Dosadila* mi je ta rutina. (I'm tired of this routine.) 
5. Do sada nismo videli tu situaciju. (We haven't seen this situation so far.)